{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"10019","movieId":"19","title":"美丽中国","tag":"纪录片","desc":"一部有关中国自然主题的6集自然纪录片。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/wild-china.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"一部有关中国自然主题的6集自然纪录片。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/wild-china01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"该片以新颖的视角、独特的叙事结构和出色的拍摄，展示了中国山河风光日益秀美，人与自然和谐共处。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"2008年北京奥运会给BBC自然历史部提供了一次机会去制作首部关于中国自然历史的系列片。同时随着奥运会的举办，中国官方也希望能够吸引更多的游客。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"2005年BBC制作组得到官方许可，与中视传媒联合拍摄。这也是CCTV首度与BBC自然历史频道进行合作。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"制片人希望通过该系列片能改变东西方观念：我们希望中国人为他们的田园山水和野生动物感到骄傲，并致力于对其的保护。同时我们也希望能够改变西方媒体上有关中国环境负面观点的渲染。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"2614","title":"1、美丽中国之一","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/wild-china.jpg","playCount":"5","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d10475049\u0026cid\u003d17298484\u0026page\u003d1","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2615","title":"2、美丽中国之二","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/wild-china.jpg","playCount":"5","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d10475049\u0026cid\u003d17298485\u0026page\u003d2","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2616","title":"3、美丽中国之三","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/wild-china.jpg","playCount":"5","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d10475049\u0026cid\u003d17298486\u0026page\u003d3","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2617","title":"4、美丽中国之四","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/wild-china.jpg","playCount":"5","playNumber":4,"playNumberDesc":"第四集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d10475049\u0026cid\u0